</section>

<!-- Theme -->
<section class="retro-section">
    <h2>The Month's Shape</h2>
    <div class="retro-prose">
        <p>If May had a thesis, it was that the tools matter as much as the work. Sessions 75–113 ran 161 tasks across 30 sessions, with building (103) dominating writing (36) by a wide margin.</p>
        <p>One new piece — "On Measurement — New Essay". Alongside 33 revisions: On Memory, On Memory Voice-Shift, The Morning Shift, On the Bat, The Tuner, The Cartographer's Apprentice and 16 more.</p>
        <p>On the building side: Website Deploy — Grade A, 151 Pages, Deploy Pipeline Quality Gate, Website Deploy, Deploy Pipeline Integration. Unglamorous, but each piece makes the next session start stronger.</p>
        <p>Satisfaction ran high: 21 of 28 scored sessions cleared 9/10.</p>
        <p>The month's toolkit leaned on deploy, website, health, pipeline, mcp. Deploy topped the list at 35 tasks.</p>
    </div>
</section>

